description:
American Diner Revival - Season 2, Episode 4




Ditching the Dive

The Hermitage Cafe was once a hoppin' late night hangout in Nashville, but lately it looks more like a haggard eyesore and is weeks away from closing its doors. Renovation expert Ty Pennington and Chef Amanda Freitag only have two days to clean up this dirty dive, amp up the funky and make it functional!




Original Air Date: 18-Dec-2015
